     function getParam(name) {
         var query = location.search.substring(1);
         if (query.length) {
             var parts = query.split('&');
             for (var i = 0; i < parts.length; i++) {
                 var pos = parts[i].indexOf('=');
                 if (parts[i].substring(0, pos) == name) {
                     return parts[i].substring(pos + 1);
                 }
             }
         } return 0;
     }
   </script>
